{
  "id": "65b38534e12b9500256521b5",
  "title": "向精神薬に関する条約",
  "created": 1706263861,
  "updated": 1706263901,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "65b38534e12b9500256521b5",
      "text": "向精神薬に関する条約",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263861,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c12f",
      "text": "[精神刺激薬]、[幻覚剤]、[向精神薬]の乱用を抑止するための[国際条約]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263865
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c130",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c131",
      "text": "> 前文",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c132",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c133",
      "text": "> 締約国は、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c134",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c135",
      "text": "> 人類の[健康]及び[福祉]に関心を有し、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c136",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c137",
      "text": "> ある種の[向精神薬]の濫用により生ずる[公衆の健康]上及び社会上の問題について懸念し、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c138",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c139",
      "text": "> これらの向精神薬の濫用及びその濫用が引き起こす不正取引を防止し、かつ、これらと戦うことを決意し、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c13a",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c13b",
      "text": "> これらの向精神薬が正当な目的に限り使用されるよう厳しい措置が必要であることを考慮し、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c13c",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c13d",
      "text": "> [向精神薬の医療上及び学術上の目的]のための使用が不可欠であること並びにこれらの目的のための向精神薬の入手が不当に制限されてはならないことを認め、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c13e",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c13f",
      "text": "> ある種の向精神薬の濫用に対する措置が効果的であるためには、協同して、かつ、世界的な規模で行動することが必要であることを信じ、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c140",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c141",
      "text": "> 向精神薬の統制の分野における[国際連合]の権限を認め、また、関係国際機関が国際連合の枠内にあることを希望し、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c142",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c143",
      "text": "> このような目的を達成するために国際条約が必要であることを認めて、",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c144",
      "text": "> ",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c145",
      "text": "> 次のとおり協定する。",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c146",
      "text": " [https://www.mhlw.go.jp/web/t_doc?dataId=97136000&dataType=0&pageNo=1 ・向精神薬に関する条約(◆平成02年09月01日条約第7号)]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c147",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c148",
      "text": " [向精神薬に関する条約のスケジュールⅠ]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c149",
      "text": "  乱用が深刻、医療価値がない",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c14a",
      "text": "  [LSD], [MDMA], [メスカリン]、[DMT], [THC]等",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c14b",
      "text": "  32物質",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c14c",
      "text": " [向精神薬に関する条約のスケジュールⅡ]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c14d",
      "text": "  乱用の危険性があり、医療価値が極小から中",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c14e",
      "text": "  [アンフェタミン], [メタンフェタミン]、[メチルフェニデート]等",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c14f",
      "text": "  46物質",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c150",
      "text": " [向精神薬に関する条約のスケジュールⅢ]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c151",
      "text": "  乱用の危険性があり、医療価値は中から極大",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c152",
      "text": "  [アモバルビタール]、[ペントバルビタール]、[フルニトラゼパム]等",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c153",
      "text": "  9物質",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c154",
      "text": " [向精神薬に関する条約のスケジュールⅣ]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c155",
      "text": "  乱用の危険性は小さい、医療価値は極小から極大",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c156",
      "text": "  [バルビタール]、[フェノバルビタール]、[ジアゼパム]、[ロラぜパム]等",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c157",
      "text": "  62物質",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3853571fa08000069c158",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263862,
      "updated": 1706263862
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3854c71fa08000069c159",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263884,
      "updated": 1706263886
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3854e71fa08000069c15b",
      "text": " [麻薬及び向精神薬取締法]",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263887,
      "updated": 1706263901
    },
    {
      "id": "65b3854c71fa08000069c15a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62c8e96f1f5ebf001d71fa08",
      "created": 1706263884,
      "updated": 1706263884
    }
  ]
}